TzHaar-Hur-Rin owns the Ore and Gem Store in Mor Ul Rek. It is also one of the few NPCs to sell uncut Onyx and Onyx bolt tips, the other being TzHaar-Hur-Lek.

Stock[edit | edit source]

The store reaches the lowest price after selling a maximum of 13 items, depending on the item.
